<item>
            <title>[THRIFT-4166] Recent fix to remove boost::lexical_cast usage broke VS2010</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/THRIFT-4166</link>
                <project id="12310800" key="THRIFT">Thrift</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Removal of boost::lexical_cast and replaced with code that calls std::log10(2).  std::log10(2) is ambiguous to VS2010.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ol&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Fix build breakage&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;add VS2010 32-bit build job to Appveyor to prevent future regression.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
</description>
