&lt;p&gt;    Appveyor died due to an environmental error getting &quot;ant&quot; with chocolatey.  I have to do an empty commit and kick another one, but I&apos;m going to wait until &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/THRIFT-4071&quot; title=&quot;Consolidate the Travis CI jobs where possible to put less stress on the Apache Foundation&amp;#39;s allocation of CI build slaves&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;THRIFT-4071&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;THRIFT-4071&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; so it isn&apos;t as expensive.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
